Chatbot

Any chatbot has three components:
Natural Language Understanding(NLU)-is about entity or actions extractions from the conversation or user query; Dialogue Management(DM)-is mainly Reinforcement Learning and is the agent(Like in AI) taking the most appropriate actions from the set of many and NLG(Natural Language Generation) converting the final action by the DM into the Human Language as a response.
TASK:
FINDING THE RIGHT DATASET(most important): The dataset should have motivational types of conversations or WHICH TRIES TO RAISE HOPE IN THE DYING PATIENT. A POSSIBLE SEARCH COULD BE: MOTIVATIONAL CONVERSATION-BASED DATASETS
Deciding the type of method which should be followed while implementing the chatbot
