Our Task Specific Resources
https://www.fingerprintforsuccess.com/blog/mental-health-chatbot mentions the mental health chatbots which help to deal with problems
From the mentioned chatbots, I tried out one Youper, it is like a flowchart where the user only gets fixed options to respond, and the output is fixed for each response. To test the robustness of the text-based answers, I am writing different inputs than expected. It considers those outputs to be ideal and generates the next ideal question.
But the point is there exist CHATBOTS FOR MENTAL HEALTH.
