General resources(could be leveraged for any problem):
There is also one framework: RASA (https://rasa.com/ )
In this framework, we just have to put the data in the required format, and then it performs all other actions.
Here intents are 
https://medium.com/voice-tech-podcast/how-to-create-chatbot-using-rasa-82954e141ae7
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1lwddP0KUEg using neural networks
NLU and DM - identifying the words which were present during the training time and putting those places as one and then feeding that vector of the sentence(representing the words of the sentence which were present during the training time) into a neural network that predicts the class or intent in which it falls. Then THE OUTPUT IS DEFINED IN THE TRAINING DATA, WHICH SHOULD BE FOR THAT PARTICULAR INTENT.


